15,01- Shadow Earth -


15,01Peace transcending,
15,01Death unending -
15,01The coffin is a relaxing bed,
15,01Pine above you, pine beneath you,
15,01Pine behind your hollow head.
15,01Like the earth that surrounds you,
15,01You are somehow without boundaries,
15,01As part of the earth you become -
15,01To the darkness, you succumb.
15,01Life to death without devision-
15,01All in all, sweet derision;
15,01Chaos realized
15,01As your thoughts are strewn awry.
15,01Pieces lost to indecision,
15,01As you strive for fresh revision,
15,01And the burning incense of time
15,01Ignites the empty flame of your hollow mind.
15,01Your essence flows into surreality
15,01As you search for elusive tranquility -
15,01In the darkness - the soul's rebirth,
15,01As you become assimilated into the shadow earth.


15,01- (c)Scimitar Wraith - GOTHiC -
